Package com.example.flexiMed.model

Class RequestEntity

java.lang.Object
com.example.flexiMed.model.RequestEntity
@Entity public class RequestEntity extends Object
Entity representing a request for ambulance services in the system. This entity captures the request details, status, timestamps, and geographical data.
